      "num": 4,
      "variant": "workflow",
      "snippet": "<div class=\"swiss-card swiss-card--body\">\n  <div class=\"swiss-card__content\">\n    \n  <div class=\"list-card list-card--workflow\">\n        <div class=\"list-card-header\"><span>标准工作流</span><span class=\"workflow-kicker\">02 / Workflow</span></div>\n        <ol>\n          <li><div><span class=\"workflow-item-title\">探索 (Explore)</span><span class=\"workflow-item-copy\">不要急于动手。先让 Claude 阅读错误日志、审查受影响代码，定位问题范围与依赖树。</span></div></li><li><div><span class=\"workflow-item-title\">规划 (Plan)</span><span class=\"workflow-item-copy\">要求 Claude 提出修复思路，在它动手前先比较实现路径与权衡。</span></div></li><li><div><span class=\"workflow-item-title\">实现 (Implement)</span><span class=\"workflow-item-copy\">明确计划后，授权 Claude 跨文件编写代码，并执行本地测试进行自我验证。</span></div></li><li><div><span class=\"workflow-item-title\">提交 (Commit)</span><span class=\"workflow-item-copy\">验证无误后，再整理为清晰的提交记录，保留可追踪的变更边界。</span></div></li>\n        </ol>\n      </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>"
